What are the treatments for throat cancer?

            #faq-content-2.accordion-collapse.collapse(data-bs-parent="#faqlist")
              .accordion-body.
                
                This varies from patient to patient and depends on the kind of cancer, itâ€™s location and stage. It also depends on the resources available at the hospital. Surgery, Radiotherapy and Chemotherapy can all play a part in treatment. Some patients will require all three modes of treatment.
                
         
